# Chrome extension architecture

- Manifest V3; minimal permissions only.
- Google Meet selectors stay in `src/adapters/google-meet/selectors.ts`.
- Analysis code must not import Chrome APIs or DOM helpers.
- Content script UI uses isolated shadow roots.
- Background worker routes typed messages only; no transcript logic yet.
